sec.p:
The results show that the test data have a large range of scatter which the maximum lifetime is 5 times plus of the minimum lifetime. The magnitude of the scatter about the experimental data may be mainly dependent on:


the deviation of DIs fixed during testing;

the inhomogeneity of the mechanical properties of the basic and added materials;

the compliance with requirements of the testing process; and

the other factors such as the errors of test device.
